        <Summary xml:lang="en">py.test plugin to abort hanging tests</Summary>
        <Description xml:lang="en">This is a plugin which will terminate tests after a certain timeout, assuming the test session isn&apos;t being debugged. When aborting a test it will show a stack dump of all threads running at the time. This is useful when running tests under a continuous integration server or simply if you don&apos;t know why the test suite hangs.
</Description>
